,"uid":33583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:03:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0137851573f976f53fdbbc3274b0fbabd4d1d909","tid":1203590,"uid":136415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jzFLZpC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjzFLZpC.png&h=0ce97ab4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e48a8cc8b3c9addb9bd0820c6f15ea984a08536e","tid":1203590,"uid":185373,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"a8f08aa767141794f9cd5b21692347d453182784","tid":1203590,"uid":9410,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:16:29.000Z","msg":"根據法例，市民若拒絕被警員即場搜身，有權要求到警署搜身，最好有證人帶往警署目擊過程。 GOOGLE搵到，係咪真？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:05:08.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n但去到警署搜 你預成晚留係警署到朝早"},{"pid":"f91459ce12da9a011d359ae6f5e011e78f32bf00","tid":1203590,"uid":33583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dd34ec5a0d24eb1ce6af8169b7e6bae59b3f929","tid":1203590,"uid":249059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"佢搜我身我都可以攞住部電話影住啲犬？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"上面巴打講<br />\n可以"},{"pid":"187356985afbb9dd82b36579e3ebfb51098cf9f7","tid":1203590,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50476bbf2075330c99241abd2630c19aab3e0ced","tid":1203590,"uid":204331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:07:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a0226a4bb4c90cd03a3ce4f6ca1251c6b9eceb","tid":1203590,"uid":138255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:09:33.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a3af11bcd73f480ac09fc88305ba8f7fd337a14e","tid":1203590,"u